# Roadmap-First Protocol
Before doing anything in this repo, READ `/docs/ROADMAP.md`.
- Identify which phase (F0..F10) the requested change belongs to.
- Confirm the phase status before writing code; if you change a phase
  outcome, update its row in the same change.
- For any new model/route/screen, also update `/docs/ADMIN-PARITY.md`
  to ensure the admin counterpart is tracked.
- Architectural decisions go to `/docs/DECISIONS.md` as a new ADR.
- Run `npm run docs:check` and include its result in your summary.
